Common Default Ports and Services

Protocol: Port:     Service:                     Encryption:
FTP       21        File Transfer                No
SSH       22        Remote Access/File Transfer  Yes
Telnet    23        Remote Access                No
SMTP      25        Email (MTA)                  No
SMB       139/445   Sharing Access
HTTP      80        WWW                          No
POP3      110       Email (MDA)                  No
IMAP      143       Email (MDA)                  No
HTTPS     443       WWW                          Yes
SMTPS     465       Email (MTA)                  Yes
FTPS      990       File Transfer                Yes
IMAPS     993       Email (MDA)                  Yes
POP3S     995       Email (MDA)                  Yes
